<li id="cite_note-EWC2015-137"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-EWC2015_137-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation book cs1"><i>The Discipline of the Evangelical Wesleyan Church</i>. <a href="/wiki/Evangelical_Wesleyan_Church" title="Evangelical Wesleyan Church">Evangelical Wesleyan Church</a>. 2015. pp.&#160;41, 57–58.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Discipline+of+the+Evangelical+Wesleyan+Church&amp;rft.pages=41%2C+57-58&amp;rft.pub=Evangelical+Wesleyan+Church&amp;rft.date=2015&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHygiene+in+Christianity" class="Z3988"></span></span>
